    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# SEO Meta Description Writer\\n\",\"**NLP Project 58 of 100** — Generate SEO-optimized titles and meta descriptions for web pages.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import re, requests\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\nprint('Loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"pages = [\\n    {'title':'How to Learn Python in 2025','keywords':['Python','learn','beginner','tutorial'],'content':'A comprehensive guide to learning Python from scratch, covering basics, data structures, and projects.'},\\n    {'title':'Best Laptops for Data Science','keywords':['laptop','data science','GPU','machine learning'],'content':'Comparison of top laptops for data science work, considering RAM, GPU, and battery life.'},\\n    {'title':'Docker for Beginners Guide','keywords':['Docker','containers','DevOps','tutorial'],'content':'Step-by-step guide to Docker, covering images, containers, volumes, and Docker Compose.'},\\n]\\n\\ndef generate_meta(page):\\n    keywords = ', '.join(page['keywords'][:3])\\n    # Title: 50-60 chars\\n    seo_title = page['title'][:60]\\n    if len(seo_title) < 50:\\n        seo_title += f' | {page[\\\"keywords\\\"][0]} Guide'\\n    seo_title = seo_title[:60]\\n    # Description: 150-160 chars\\n    desc = page['content'][:130]\\n    desc += f' Learn {keywords}.'\\n    desc = desc[:160]\\n    return {'title': seo_title, 'description': desc, 'title_len': len(seo_title), 'desc_len': len(desc)}\\n\\nfor page in pages:\\n    meta = generate_meta(page)\\n    print(f'Page: {page[\\\"title\\\"]}')\\n    print(f'  SEO Title ({meta[\\\"title_len\\\"]} chars): {meta[\\\"title\\\"]}')\\n    print(f'  Meta Desc ({meta[\\\"desc_len\\\"]} chars): {meta[\\\"description\\\"]}')\\n    print()\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **SEO titles should be 50-60 characters** with primary keyword near the start.\\n\",\"- **Meta descriptions should be 150-160 characters** with a clear value proposition.\\n\",\"- **Template-based generation ensures consistency**; LLMs add creativity.\\n\",\"- **For production, A/B test titles** and track click-through rates.\"]}\n",
    " ],\n",
